CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 16, 1949, pg. 3 reads: "Flag Ceremony - The Hi-Y Club of Schenley High School presented a new flag to the school Wednesday morning. Clifford Jackson, chairman of the committee, made the presentation to Principal Bernard J. McCormick.  Left to right are: Clifford Paige, Barney Kessler, president of the club, who made a short speech during the program; Alphonse Nowlan, Williams Fisher, Allen Meyer, Clifford Jackson, Andrew Laird and Mr. McCormick. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Members of the Hi-Y Club of Schenley High School, from left: Clifford Paige, Barney Kessler, Alphonse Nowlan, Williams Fisher, Allen Meyer, Clifford Jackson, and Andrew Laird, presenting new flag to Schenley High School Principle Bernard J. McCormick
